snippet.title: Covert Syndrome - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Covert Syndrome on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/589460/

Covert Syndrome is a free to play Coop corridor shooter with a focus on unscripted AI and fast tough combat. Created as an prototyping project we wanted to release it to the community so people can experience Co-op VR for free.

Games reviews and download: http://download.online-games.co/
